## Acknowledgments

This macOS adaptation maintains full respect and attribution to the original 
creators of the Black Hole physics simulation:

- **kavan010 (Kavan)** - [@squee72564](https://github.com/squee72564)
- **Alexander Rodriguez** - [@CaseyChesshir](https://github.com/CaseyChesshir)
- **Casey Chesshir** - [@CaseyChesshir](https://github.com/CaseyChesshir)

Original project video explanation: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8-B6ryuBkCM

The macOS adaptations include OpenGL compatibility modifications, build system 
updates, and platform-specific optimizations while preserving the original 
physics implementation and creative work.